      "patchset_number": 11,
      "line": 40,
      "message": "This needs to respect the phase argument passed into the script, and not run this every time.  According to the pom.xml in this directory, this can be invoked for the clean, generate-sources, compile, package, test, install, and deploy phases.  As is, this will do a complete build-and-install every time it is invoked.",
